parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger seat occupancy sensor can cause the passenger airbag to be disabled, which can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The passenger airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag may not deploy in an accident
the light may come on and off randomly
the light may stay on continuously
the sensor may malfunction when a person is sitting in the passenger seat
the warning light may not turn off even when the passenger seat is empty.
